lourish and we constantly challenge each other to improve it’s exciting to work with our customers on new technologies that help them grow” mark williams vp marketing  north america gilbarco veederroot joined the fortive family in  kaizen empowers me to work with our customers on a much deeper level than what our competitors can do” gideon fick fortive business system fbs leader gilbarco veederroot joined the fortive family in  “sometimes we see things that our customers can’t even articulate but it isn’t about our customers telling us what they want it’s about us understanding enough of what they’re trying to accomplish so we can come up with something better” barbara hulit svp joined the fortive family in  accelerating progress fortive is a global family of more than  industryleading companies united by a shared purpose essential technology for the people who accelerate progress from transportation and precision automation to breakthrough consumer experiences we take on big challenges with real impact teletrac navman helped domino’s pizza enhance its mobile app with global positioning system gps tracking capability customers can track their pizza from creation to delivery and domino’s benefits from improved operational efficiency and safety  we know the only way to achieve our shared purpose is through our people—great people equipped with proven tools and an environment that enables them to seize opportunities imagine the next breakthrough and create the next innovation a community that cares “we’ve hosted students here on campus who come and learn about engineering i always see students’ eyes light up we actually sort of had to kick them out at the end of the class” graham mccarthy tektronix joined the fortive family in  the culture of giving at tektronix is a source of pride and joy for its employees the tektronix foundation supports a number of community charities including susan g komen race for the cure and stem classes for youth employees are allotted paid time each quarter for volunteer work and many extend their volunteer commitments to their own time as well fortive companies have a culture of caring which benefits employees as well as those they help join our extraordinary team fortive is a place where exceptional people work fortive offers opportunities at all levels in a wide range of departments including human resources engineering marketing sales and finance at its corporate headquarters in everett washington and throughout its family of operating companies worldwide we are proud to offer you and your family a variety of benefits—it’s a key aspect of what makes our company a great place to work your particular benefits package will depend on your position location and years with the company here’s a look at what you might be eligible for health insurance life insurance accident insurance disability insurance retirement savings plan with company contribution paid vacations and holidays onsite fitness centerfitness discounts tuition assistance every fortive employee enjoys unique opportunities to learn from the best and grow in an exciting culture of continuous improvement we invite you to explore open positions from internships to technical and managerial roles to executive leadership explore opportunities fortive and danaher steven and mitchell rales  fortive skip to main content stock info header contact suppliers search toggle navigation search social hero image desktop hero image mobile hero image tablet our history fortive the essential technology company although fortive is a new company our roots run deep our portfolio is built with strong brands that are established leaders in the markets they serve our operating companies have long histories of solving customers’ critical needs and our heritage dates back to the earliest days of the globally renowned danaher corporation this singular combination of past success and forwardfocused innovation makes fortive uniquely positioned to create implement and accelerate progress   foundation in the early s steven and mitchell rales envisioned a manufacturing company dedicated to continuous improvement and customer satisfaction which led to the creation of danaher danaher was one of the first companies in north america to adopt the principles of kaizen a japanese philosophy of continuous improvement and its unique and rigorous interpretation of this approach shaped the danaher business system dbs fortive’s leaders have deep experience overseeing and implementing dbs and will continue to guide its evolution as the fortive business system fbs our business will evolve but the guiding principles of fbs—continuous improvement and customer satisfaction—remain steadfast   focus one of the keys to danaher’s success was its creation of strategic platforms each with sustainable competitive advantages and leadership positions in attractive markets over the years danaher’s portfolio evolved into an increasingly global growthoriented set of scientific and technological businesses generating over b in revenue in  in july  danaher separated into two independent publicly traded companies danaher and fortive fortive is now a focused industrial growth company driving innovation in the areas of field instrumentation transportation sensing product realization automation and specialty and franchise distribution   future fortive’s  global employees are united by a shared culture and led by experienced executives with over  years of combined danaher experience we are agile inquisitive innovators who draw upon our strong tradition of success everything we do is designed for a world that thrives on speed and rigor and we are deeply committed to delivering essential technology that makes the world stronger safer and better we are passionate about powering progress at a global scale to advance the greater good this is our vision for the future—the vision were aggressively pursuing—as we build a global diversified industrial growth company to drive the