 each one helps make the world stronger safer and better we work together to make progress where it’s needed the most accelerating breakthrough innovation in fastmoving fields like software development robotics transportation energy and healthcare we are united by a shared purpose and values and by our commitment to making an impact on the world at fortive you can work with and learn from great people in a vibrant culture defined by opportunity empowerment and continuous learning and growth we are a set of extraordinary teams working together to achieve extraordinary things we are fortive our shared purpose our innovation it’s not every day that your company can say “this is an industry first” but tektronix’ new  series mso redefines oscilloscopes with  industry first innovations delivering unprecedented flexibility and unmatched visibility into complex embedded systems this is the first product in a series of introductions as part of our platform developed with the new tek chip congratulations to everyone for all the hard work on bringing this product to market this is world class innovation and tektronix is leading the way learn more fortive operating companies fortives portfolio of businesses spans the globe and their innovations surround each of us daily in the form of essential technology they keep power grids and factories running support the largest data centers advance robotics through precision motion and automation and drive the global economy by ensuring safe efficient transport of goods each of our operating companies is working to accelerate breakthrough innovation in its field fluke is the world leader in the manufacture distribution and service of electronic test tools biomedical equipment and networking solutions kollmorgen designs and manufactures motion systems and components for a wide variety of industries worldwide thomson is a world leader in precision mechanical motion technology portescap designs and manufactures precise compact motors for use in the medical and aerospace industries dynapar offers the worlds broadest range of encoders resolvers and accessories for motion feedback control jacobs vehicle systems is a leader in engine braking technology trusted by the worlds most wellknown engine manufacturers matco tools is a manufacturer and distributor of quality professional automotive repair tools and diagnostic equipment hennessy industries manufactures wheelservice equipment for the automotive industry with its ammco coats baseline and bada brands west control solutions is an industryleading manufacturer of temperature control process control and automation products at qualitrol we are redefining condition based monitoring technology for electric utilities assets gilbarco veederroot supplies fuel dispensers and pointofsale technology for convenience stores and gas stations tektronix designs and manufactures test and measurement equipment accelerating global innovation in industries such as communications health and aerospace invetech helps companies bring new products to market with its product realization and automation consulting services pacific scientific is an engineering company providing missioncritical solutions for the aerospace and defense industries gems sensors  controls is a global manufacturer of customized sensors switches controls and valves setra systems designs and manufactures an array of electronic instruments that measure pressure acceleration and weight andersonnegele provides hygienic instrumentation sensors for the food and life sciences industries teletrac navman provides cloudbased gps fleettracking software for the trucking industry view all community impact fortive’s culture of caring at specialty product technologies was evident in the harrowing week following hurricane matthew at every level of the company people helped each other fortive sent truckloads of food and donations to the united way company managers personally checked in with each associate and communicated a “family first work second” mentality team members helped each other with bedding and clothing donations careers at fortive at fortive there’s no limit to what you can learn or the impact you can make and there’s no need to choose between the excitement of a startup and the opportunities made possible by a global business with a strong history of success at fortive you can work with and learn from the best explore financial news fortive to present at the william blair growth stock conferencefortive hosts investor day reaffirms second quarter and fullyear  guidancefortive to present at electrical products group conferencefortive reports first quarter  resultsfortive to webcast investor dayfortive declares regular dividendfortive schedules first quarter  earnings conference callfortive to present at the bank of america merrill lynch global industrials  eu autos conferencefortive to present at jp morgan aviation transportation and industrials conferencefortive to present at the barclays industrial select conferencefortive reports fourth quarter  results and initiates  guidancefortive declares regular dividendfortive schedules fourth quarter  earnings conference callfortive to present at the credit suisse th annual industrials conferencefortive declares regular dividendfortive to present at bairds  industrial conferencefortive reports third quarter  resultsfortive schedules third quarter  earnings conference callfortive to present at morgan stanley th annual laguna conferencefortive to present at vertical research partners industrial conferencefortive declares regular dividendfortive reports second quarter  resultsfortive completes separation from danaher and launches as an independent publicly traded companyfortive schedules second quarter  earnings conference callfortive announces equity investor meetings for upcoming spinoff from danaher and provides financial outlook as standalone companyfortive to present at the william blair growth stock conferencefortive hosts in